All the ladies in town
want him for a husband.

00:10:50.650 --> 00:10:52.652 position:50% align:center
His one flaw is his soft heart.

00:10:52.736 --> 00:10:54.529 position:50% align:center
Wow, he sounds great.

00:10:54.612 --> 00:10:56.322 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I had no idea.

00:10:56.406 --> 00:10:57.615 position:50% align:center
[yells]

00:10:57.699 --> 00:10:59.993 position:50% align:center
But, as many people do,

00:11:00.076 --> 00:11:03.455 position:50% align:center
he has a sorrowful past
that still pains him.

00:11:03.538 --> 00:11:05.290 position:50% align:center
When he was just ten years old,

00:11:05.373 --> 00:11:07.625 position:50% align:center
his mother disappeared
from his life.

00:11:07.709 --> 00:11:08.793 position:50% align:center
[BOTH gasp]

00:11:08.877 --> 00:11:10.628 position:50% align:center
[yells]

00:11:11.796 --> 00:11:14.799 position:50% align:center
[HATSUHARU] It was cold
outside and pouring rain.

00:11:14.883 --> 00:11:18.219 position:50% align:center
She gently covered him with
a hand-knitted sweater.

00:11:18.303 --> 00:11:21.806 position:50% align:center
Her soft hands. Her sweet voice.

00:11:21.890 --> 00:11:26.102 position:50% align:center
The tears spilling
down her cheeks.

00:11:26.186 --> 00:11:28.063 position:50% align:center
That was what he remembered.

00:11:28.146 --> 00:11:31.191 position:50% align:center
The last memory he
had of his mother.

00:11:33.318 --> 00:11:36.404 position:50% align:center
[HATSUHARU]
The next morning, she was gone.

00:11:36.488 --> 00:11:39.491 position:50% align:center
The little boy was left
with his alcoholic father,

00:11:39.574 --> 00:11:44.371 position:50% align:center
an enormous amount of debt,
and that hand-knitted sweater.

00:11:44.454 --> 00:11:47.791 position:50% align:center
However, he believed in his
mother's tears that night,

00:11:47.874 --> 00:11:50.877 position:50% align:center
and would never bear
a grudge against her.

00:11:50.960 --> 00:11:52.253 position:50% align:center
[yells]

00:11:52.337 --> 00:11:55.799 position:50% align:center
And so, he worked hard
and lived frugally

00:11:55.882 --> 00:11:59.678 position:50% align:center
until he was finally able
to repay his father's debt.

00:11:59.761 --> 00:12:02.180 position:50% align:center
At night, he would
embrace the sweater

00:12:02.263 --> 00:12:04.224 position:50% align:center
his mother had left behind

00:12:04.307 --> 00:12:06.518 position:50% align:center
and dream of the day
he would be able

00:12:06.601 --> 00:12:08.978 position:50% align:center
to see her face once again.

00:12:09.062 --> 00:12:10.230 position:50% align:center
[yells]

00:12:10.313 --> 00:12:11.940 position:50% align:center
That day is today.

00:12:12.023 --> 00:12:13.900 position:50% align:center
His mother is coming
here to see him.

00:12:13.983 --> 00:12:14.943 position:50% align:center
[MOMIJI, TOHRU gasp]

00:12:15.026 --> 00:12:17.278 position:50% align:center
What are you guys
doing over here?

00:12:17.362 --> 00:12:20.281 position:50% align:center
She wouldn't have abandoned the
young son she loved so deeply

00:12:20.365 --> 00:12:21.533 position:50% align:center
if she hadn't been desperate,

00:12:21.616 --> 00:12:24.327 position:50% align:center
but in time, she came
to regret the decision

00:12:24.411 --> 00:12:26.413 position:50% align:center
she had made that night.

00:12:26.496 --> 00:12:30.041 position:50% align:center
And today, she'll tell her son
in her own words why she left.

00:12:30.125 --> 00:12:33.128 position:50% align:center
[screaming]

00:12:33.211 --> 00:12:34.963 position:50% align:center
[KYO, YUKI gasp]

00:12:35.046 --> 00:12:36.256 position:50% align:center
A touching reunion.

00:12:36.339 --> 00:12:38.091 position:50% align:center
You can't do that!

00:12:38.174 --> 00:12:39.467 position:50% align:center
They're together again.

00:12:39.551 --> 00:12:41.428 position:50% align:center
I know! It's so beautiful!

00:12:41.511 --> 00:12:42.887 position:50% align:center
[HATSUHARU]
All's well that ends well.

00:12:42.971 --> 00:12:44.973 position:50% align:center
[KYO]
What the hell, Haru? You idiot!

00:12:45.056 --> 00:12:47.976 position:50% align:center
You can't just go around
breaking stuff like that!

00:12:48.059 --> 00:12:49.769 position:50% align:center
[YUKI groans]

00:12:49.853 --> 00:12:53.523 position:50% align:center
[MANAGER A] Honestly,
I should call your parents.

00:12:53.606 --> 00:12:56.234 position:50% align:center
Make them pay for the damage.

00:12:56.317 --> 00:12:58.486 position:50% align:center
[MANAGER A] They've got such
angelic faces, though.

00:12:58.570 --> 00:13:01.281 position:50% align:center
Are these kids
models or something?

00:13:01.364 --> 00:13:02.782 position:50% align:center
[MANAGER A] Stay here.
I'll be back in a minute.

00:13:02.866 --> 00:13:04.325 position:50% align:center
Wait, sir!

00:13:04.409 --> 00:13:06.161 position:50% align:center
We'll pay whatever you want,

00:13:06.244 --> 00:13:08.955 position:50% align:center
