00:21:03.388 --> 00:21:06.224 position:50% align:center
But, Tohru, weren't you scared?

00:21:06.307 --> 00:21:07.517 position:50% align:center
It was very moving.

00:21:07.600 --> 00:21:08.977 position:50% align:center
It really was!

00:21:09.060 --> 00:21:11.688 position:50% align:center
Moving? A haunted house?

00:21:11.771 --> 00:21:14.524 position:50% align:center
[BOTH]
More like exhausting.

00:21:14.607 --> 00:21:17.610 position:50% align:center
I know! I'm tearing up
just thinking about it.

00:21:17.694 --> 00:21:21.990 position:50% align:center
Wow. It must've been quite
an unusual haunted house.

00:21:22.073 --> 00:21:26.077 position:50% align:center
Anyway, it sounds like the break
is off to a promising start.

00:21:26.161 --> 00:21:29.372 position:50% align:center
Yes! And I'm sure it's
only going to get better!

00:21:29.456 --> 00:21:33.126 position:50% align:center
I've never been more excited
about summer vacation before!

00:21:36.713 --> 00:21:43.636 position:50% align:center
[KURENO] If I could...
I'd stay by your side forever.

00:21:43.720 --> 00:21:45.930 position:50% align:center
To hear your laugh.

00:21:47.390 --> 00:21:50.643 position:50% align:center
[KURENO]
To see your smile.

00:21:50.727 --> 00:21:52.979 position:50% align:center
To taste your lips.

00:21:59.944 --> 00:22:03.198 position:50% align:center
[AKITO]
Welcome home, Kureno.

00:22:03.281 --> 00:22:07.118 position:50% align:center
You didn't get into any trouble
while you were out, did you?

00:22:11.539 --> 00:22:14.668 position:50% align:center
Of course not, Akito.

00:22:17.879 --> 00:22:23.176 position:50% align:center
[KURENO] But... I doubt
I'll ever see you again.

00:23:57.312 --> 00:24:00.523 position:50% align:center
[SHIGURE] "Then are you
really this stupid?"